summary: This mod Adds More Eyes For your Character more color Variants
descriptionHtml:
This mod adds 40 elven eyes 30 orc eyes 15 human eyes and 40 beast eyes


Change Log 
_______________________________________________________________________

v1.02 human  eye colors is finished  and other eyes stand in line
        2 more eyes for orc and elf\'s are now added

v1.01-B  adds blind eyes on left and right sided + some 2 diffrent colored eyes + alot of new color  variation for all the races
fixed some of the eyes  for  the 2 diffrent colors also this should work on custom races thats uses RaceElf - headparts to these eyes

v1.00  added 25 elven eyes 11 orc eyes 9 human eyes and 20 beast eyes
_______________________________________________________________________

info :

This pack does not replace any eye textures ingame  this adds new eyes ingame and uses its own textures

and youre free to replace the textures in this pack and  upload it on any site  but  do not change the  main file for the eyes and always credit me for the esp file and try keep in mind send me a note about your mod when its finished
